main event: A flash of light was observed over a forest, interpreted as an astronomical meteor sighting.
interesting points: The sighting lasted for approximately 10 to 15 seconds., The object was described to be delta wing-shaped and about the size of a piece of paper., The object moved in a 70-degree arc within 10 seconds., The report concludes the sighting was likely a meteor based on the given observations., No sound was associated with the sighting.
